<i>[Tian Peilan, Voice message]</i>

30
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:58,120
Why did Tian Peilan send me so many messages?

31
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:59,280
What's wrong?

32
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:04,672
Dad and mom

33
00:02:05,320 --> 00:02:07,040
only care about the baby now,

34
00:02:07,760 --> 00:02:08,919
don't care about me at all.

35
00:02:10,160 --> 00:02:11,680
They abandon Blue now,

36
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:14,528
next,

37
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,160
