69
00:03:48,820 --> 00:03:50,600
Really? That's good, then.

70
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,920
<i>That pinch is killing me.</i>

71
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:54,440
<i>You fool.</i>

72
00:03:57,400 --> 00:04:01,600
Feifei, look, we are also having a baby.

73
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:03,800
<i>Why do you always have to</i>

74
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,320
<i>drag me into something so childish?</i>

75
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:07,640
No matter what happens to him,

76
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:09,400
