77
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,080
Right, honey?

78
00:04:12,320 --> 00:04:13,860
Of course.

79
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:15,340
<i>Honey?</i>

80
00:04:15,340 --> 00:04:18,280
<i>Whatever, if you say so.</i>

81
00:04:18,280 --> 00:04:21,420
