87
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,640
<i>Your honey thinks it makes sense.</i>

88
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:34,840
He and I

89
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:36,240
run a pet hospital.

90
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:39,200
You let me meet your parents,

91
00:04:39,200 --> 00:04:40,800
and I'll convince them

92
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:43,040
not to send away Blue, okay?

93
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:48,280
