94
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,080
We are all adults.

95
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:52,400
Why do we lie to a child, right?

96
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,120
Who is it?

97
00:04:57,120 --> 00:04:58,208
It's so late.

98
00:04:58,880 --> 00:05:00,480
It could be my delivery.

99
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:03,360
Could you check for me, honey?

100
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:06,920
<i>Okay, honey.</i>

101
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:10,700
Alright, I-I'll go get it now.

102
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:11,800
I'll go get it now.

103
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,200
<i>Let's see.</i>

104
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,520
Tian Tian, it's me.

105
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:22,720
<i>Tian Peilan, why is she here?</i>

106
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,960
Is it a delivery?

107
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,792
Honey.

108
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:28,760
<i>What, honey?</i>

109
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,320
<i>Honey.</i>

110
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:41,160
I've sent so many messages
and you didn't respond,

111
