121
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:32,320
Two months ago?

122
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:36,120
<i>Shen Mi, you are good.</i>

123
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:40,440
Didn't you just move here?

124
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,680
<i>Amazing, Tian Tian.</i>

125
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,160
<i>You really can keep a secret.</i>

126
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:51,600
Is your morning sickness very bad?

127
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,840
<i>You brat.</i>

128
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:02,020
Kid, wait.

129
00:07:02,020 --> 00:07:05,020
I-I-I need you to repeat what you just said.

130
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:07,160
I asked her if the morning sickness is bad.

131
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:09,480
I remember my mom throwing up a lot

132
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,840
when she's pregnant with my sister.

133
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,008
Are you pregnant?

134
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:24,240
Keep it down.

135
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,520
I-I am pregnant

136
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:27,680
for two months.

137
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,696
What's wrong?

138
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:38,340
Nothing.

139
00:07:38,340 --> 00:07:41,360
Is this aunt all right?

140
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:43,616
