141
00:07:46,200 --> 00:07:47,480
I have something to do,

142
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:51,040
or I'll leave now.

143
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,640
- I'm going to go.
- I'll send you off.

144
00:07:53,160 --> 00:07:54,160
- I'll send you off.
- No, no.

145
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,320
Just take good care of Tian Tian.

146
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:58,560
You two should be together.

147
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,048
<i>I'm leaving.</i>

148
00:08:02,048 --> 00:08:04,720
<i>Brother, sister-in-law,
our Tian Tian has found her Mr. Right.</i>

149
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,960
It's already late.

150
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,920
Feifei, you should go to sleep.

151
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:34,880
Yes, it's so late.

152
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,240
You should go to bed.

153
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,200
Well…

154
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,039
Why don't you…

155
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:47,640
No, you can sleep on our bed.

156
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:49,520
Then where do you sleep?

157
00:08:50,112 --> 00:08:51,168
I…

158
00:08:51,168 --> 00:08:52,400
You don't need to worry about us.

159
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,560
We…

160
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,460
Y-You just need to take care of yourself.

161
00:08:55,460 --> 00:08:56,960
Go brush your teeth then go to sleep.

162
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,240
No.

163
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,520
Why not?

164
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,360
