so you can't sleep on the sofa.

165
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,680
My mom is pregnant,

166
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:06,360
and my dad is really careful.

167
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:08,480
He would always tuck pillows

168
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,760
under my mother's calves at night.

169
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,680
I'll just sleep on the sofa today.

170
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:13,760
Are you sure?

171
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,480
You two

172
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,880
go back to your rooms and sleep.

173
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,520
Then you'd get a good night's sleep.
Good night.

174
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,520
- Good night.
- You're so considerate.

175
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,096
Sister,

176
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:29,840
could you stay until I fall asleep?

177
00:09:29,840 --> 00:09:32,400
Why? Are you scared?

178
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:36,000
You're a grown boy.

179
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:40,120
I-I'm not scared at all.

180
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:43,000
I-It's the first time I sleep out.

181
00:09:43,000 --> 00:09:44,480
I can't fall asleep.

182
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:47,580
You can't fall asleep. I have a solution.

183
00:09:47,580 --> 00:09:49,680
He'd read you a bedtime story

184
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:50,920
to get you to sleep, how's that?

185
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,800
I've grown up.

186
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:56,080
I don't need the bedtime story.

187
00:09:56,920 --> 00:09:59,000
Why not? It's very interesting.

188
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:01,536
I want to hear it. Right, honey?

189
00:10:01,536 --> 00:10:02,560
<i>Honey.</i>

190
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:04,520
I don't care what you want to hear.

191
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:07,840
I can only tell Pinocchio.
Do you want to hear it?

192
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,680
That's too childish.

193
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,800
Can you change another one?

194
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:13,960
Why are you so demanding?

195
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,440
I only know Pinocchio. Take it or leave it.

196
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:17,000
- You can sleep by yourself.
- No, no.

197
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,680
We'd like to hear this one.

198
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:22,440
F-Fine.

199
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:25,640
Don't you want it?

200
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,960
Don't argue with a child.

201
00:10:34,144 --> 00:10:35,200
A long time ago,

202
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:38,280
there was an old man
named Gepetto living in a village.

203
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:40,920
Mr. Gepetto was a craftsman,

204
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:42,840
who could carve

205
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:45,920
all kinds of wooden puppets.

206
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:12,280
So, they lived happily ever after.

207
00:11:35,160 --> 00:11:37,120
I'm done with the story. You'd handle the rest.

208
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,880
You're such a hypnotic storyteller.

209
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,400
Could you tell more in the future?

210
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:54,280
You are perfect today.

211
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:10,480
If he doesn't give me information
about his family tomorrow,

212
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,980
I'll call the police.

213
00:12:11,980 --> 00:12:13,360
Don't.

214
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:16,200
I think Feifei might
have misunderstood his parents.

215
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:18,720
He seems like a good boy.

216
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:20,120
We'll talk to him tomorrow,

217
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:21,280
and I'm sure he would tell.

218
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:26,080
He's not like someone to

219
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,380
bully her younger brother.

220
00:12:27,380 --> 00:12:30,160
Why do you say so?

221
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,840
W-What are you doing?

222
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:39,360
Go to bed now.

223
00:12:40,240 --> 00:12:41,280
I…

224
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,800
Okay, thank you.

225
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,040
Why don't you sleep?

226
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,600
You too.

227
00:13:56,800 --> 00:14:00,000
I saw you peeking at me,

228
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,920
are you planning something against me?

229
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:04,960
What?

230
00:14:07,040 --> 00:14:08,440
I didn't.

231
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,740
I've been thinking,

232
00:14:09,740 --> 00:14:11,400
it's been a long time,

233
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:13,480
and I haven't

234
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:15,880
really said thank you.

235
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:32,340
Thank you for helping Tianlin
when it was in trouble,

236
00:14:32,340 --> 00:14:34,040
helping the hospital through the crisis,

237
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:35,640
and saving Tianlin's reputation.

238
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:38,400
Anything else?

239
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,920
And thank you for your dedication

240
00:14:40,920 --> 00:14:43,840
to the management of our hospital.

241
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:46,976
Indeed,

242
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:48,920
for all of you,

243
00:14:48,920 --> 00:14:50,480
I am truly worried.

244
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:52,520
I just said something nice about you,

245
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:54,360
why can't you say something good back?

246
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:56,128
Nothing else?

247
00:14:57,760 --> 00:15:00,720
And you've helped me a lot,

248
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:04,080
making me a qualified director and operator.

249
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:07,760
To tell you the truth,

250
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:08,864
I think

251
00:15:10,040 --> 00:15:11,520
you're still a long way

252
00:15:12,520 --> 00:15:14,120
from being qualified,

253
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:16,160
need to work harder.

254
00:15:16,680 --> 00:15:20,160
If you say that, then I stop talking.

255
00:15:20,160 --> 00:15:22,000
Didn't you just say to thank you?

256
00:15:22,760 --> 00:15:24,180
Why do you stop?

257
00:15:24,180 --> 00:15:25,200
Anyway,

258
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:27,080
I am still a long way from being qualified.

259
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:28,760
So let's talk about it when I am qualified.

260
00:15:28,760 --> 00:15:29,840
Good night, I'm going to sleep first.

261
00:16:21,952 --> 00:16:25,728
<i>[Tianlin Animal Hospital]</i>

262
00:16:26,880 --> 00:16:28,640
Sister, are you sure

263
00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:29,960
my parents won't send Blue away?

264
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:32,880
Don't worry. I will convince your parents.

265
00:16:34,520 --> 00:16:35,552
Right?

266
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,344
Of course.

267
00:16:41,800 --> 00:16:43,040
Mirror, mirror on the wall,

268
00:16:44,040 --> 00:16:47,120
tell me who the most handsome man
in Tianlin Hospital is.

269
00:16:48,160 --> 00:16:50,560
You don't have to say, I know it must be me.

270
00:16:50,560 --> 00:16:52,200
Then tell me,

271
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:54,840
does Tian Tian like the handsome me,

272
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:57,240
or that sarcastic Shen Mi?

273
00:16:58,640 --> 00:17:00,880
I also know it must be me.

274
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:04,640
Bro,

275
00:17:05,240 --> 00:17:06,839
since you fell in love with my sister,

276
00:17:06,839 --> 00:17:08,680
what's the matter with your intelligence?

277
00:17:08,680 --> 00:17:10,240
Have you ever been in love?

278
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:13,800
Intelligence doesn't matter at all in love.

279
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:15,480
What's important is love.

280
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:16,760
Understand?

281
00:17:16,760 --> 00:17:19,400
When you're in love,

282
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:21,740
- the resistance--
- Must be strong.

283
00:17:21,740 --> 00:17:25,088
Like me, the more setbacks, the more courage.

284
00:17:27,280 --> 00:17:30,060
Wait. Why are you sighing?

285
00:17:30,060 --> 00:17:31,520
Just say it.

286
00:17:31,520 --> 00:17:33,000
Something big happened.

287
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:35,712
What happened?

288
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:39,480
Feifei, you silly boy.

289
00:17:39,480 --> 00:17:41,320
How could you run away from home?

290
00:17:41,320 --> 00:17:43,280
You scared me to death, do you know?

291
00:17:44,600 --> 00:17:47,160
Feifei, you go out with mom first.

292
00:17:47,840 --> 00:17:50,600
Dad might have something to talk to them.

293
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:52,160
Shall we go to the car first?

294
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:53,568
- Be good, let's go.
- I'm not leaving.

295
00:17:53,568 --> 00:17:54,600
Come on.

296
00:17:54,600 --> 00:17:57,920
Feifei, be good and go out with mom.

297
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:01,000
Mom can't stay here for long.

298
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:03,080
I'm not leaving. You all
just want to abandon Blue.

299
00:18:03,080 --> 00:18:04,440
I want Blue to be with me.

300
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:05,760
What's wrong with you?

301
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:07,120
- Come here.
- I'm not leaving.

302
00:18:08,280 --> 00:18:09,280
I'm sorry

303
00:18:09,280 --> 00:18:10,680
to cause you so much trouble.

304
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:11,744
It's okay.

305
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:14,240
Actually, Feifei

306
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:16,340
told me something about your family.

307
00:18:16,340 --> 00:18:18,480
Maybe there's been a lot of misunderstanding.

308
00:18:20,360 --> 00:18:22,800
In fact, whether there is
a pregnant woman or a baby at home,

309
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:24,000
you can still keep pets,

310
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:26,060
especially animals like cats and dogs.

311
00:18:26,060 --> 00:18:27,120
Really?

312
00:18:27,120 --> 00:18:28,128
Yes.

313
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:29,880
I gave Blue a checkup

314
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:31,000
and it is very healthy.

315
00:18:31,800 --> 00:18:33,520
And your defenses against Toxoplasma

316
00:18:33,520 --> 00:18:34,880
may have gone too far.

317
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:36,880
Actually, I gave Blue a checkup yesterday

318
00:18:36,880 --> 00:18:38,540
and it's not infected with Toxoplasma.

319
00:18:38,540 --> 00:18:40,120
And as long as you get it vaccinated,

320
00:18:40,120 --> 00:18:41,240
don't feed it raw meat,

321
00:18:41,240 --> 00:18:43,320
and minimizes its contact
with the outside world,

322
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:46,000
you can prevent problems with parasites.

323
00:18:47,080 --> 00:18:48,096
Well…

324
00:18:48,920 --> 00:18:50,500
- Look.
- Yes, look.

325
00:18:50,500 --> 00:18:52,360
Did Blue get this thing

326
00:18:52,360 --> 00:18:53,720
on my wife?

327
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:59,120
This isn't ringworm,

328
00:18:59,120 --> 00:19:00,600
should be some ordinary dermatitis.

329
00:19:01,184 --> 00:19:03,820
Don't worry, and Blue is very healthy.

330
00:19:03,820 --> 00:19:05,280
It doesn't even have ringworm,

331
00:19:05,280 --> 00:19:06,920
so it couldn't infect you.

332
00:19:07,800 --> 00:19:09,080
But,

333
00:19:09,080 --> 00:19:10,880
I wonder if Blue would hurt the baby

334
00:19:10,880 --> 00:19:12,480
after she's born.

335
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:15,600
Well, cats are very sensitive

336
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:17,040
to human emotions.

337
00:19:17,040 --> 00:19:18,320
As long as you don't attack it,

338
00:19:18,320 --> 00:19:20,320
it won't actively attack humans.

339
00:19:20,320 --> 00:19:21,880
And now domestic cats

340
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:23,480
are very close to humans,

341
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:24,720
even there are babies in the family,

342
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:26,160
they won't hurt them.

343
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:27,680
But…

344
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:31,880
Tian, bring Blue to them.

345
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:41,920
Feifei's parents,

346
00:19:41,920 --> 00:19:43,780
actually, the main reason

347
00:19:43,780 --> 00:19:45,000
why Feifei ran away from home

348
00:19:45,000 --> 00:19:46,680
is you guys wanted to abandon Blue,

349
00:19:46,680 --> 00:19:47,760
which broke his heart.

350
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:51,400
And he thinks you don't love
or care about him anymore

351
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:54,220
when he finds out mom's pregnant.

352
00:19:54,220 --> 00:19:56,720
This might be the real reason.

353
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,520
Silly boy.

354
00:19:59,080 --> 00:20:00,080
Do you know

355
00:20:00,080 --> 00:20:02,200
you are the apple of my and your dad's eyes?

356
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:04,120
We really, really love you.

357
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:06,048
Feifei.

358
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:08,140
When your mom gave birth to you,

359
00:20:08,140 --> 00:20:09,680
it took ten hours,

360
00:20:10,560 --> 00:20:12,440
she even passed out a few times.

361
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:15,720
Feifei.

362
00:20:15,720 --> 00:20:17,792
You should blame me.

363
00:20:18,520 --> 00:20:20,640
It's my fault for not
taking good care of you for mom.

364
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:22,400
It's all my fault.

365
00:20:27,800 --> 00:20:28,832
Feifei.

366
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:31,680
Boy, why are you so silly

367
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:33,520
to think that mom and dad would abandon you?

368
00:20:34,040 --> 00:20:35,280
Feifei, you know what?

369
00:20:35,280 --> 00:20:37,820
Whether it is you or the baby inside me,

370
00:20:37,820 --> 00:20:39,320
you are all the most important children

371
00:20:39,320 --> 00:20:41,200
for me and your dad,

372
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:43,520
and we can't lose any of you.

373
00:20:43,520 --> 00:20:44,920
Do you know it, Feifei?

374
00:20:55,560 --> 00:20:57,800
See, I didn't lie to you.

375
00:20:57,800 --> 00:20:59,820
Your parents really love you.

376
00:20:59,820 --> 00:21:01,280
Thank you for taking care of Feifei.

377
00:21:01,840 --> 00:21:03,160
I will never think of

378
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,640
sending Blue away again.

379
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:07,400
- You can't think of that anymore.
- Thank you.

380
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:09,760
Tian Tian.

381
00:21:13,080 --> 00:21:14,160
Are you pregnant?

382
00:21:20,920 --> 00:21:21,960
Yes.

383
00:21:27,520 --> 00:21:28,640
<i>[Tianlin Animal Hospital]</i>
Thank you.

384
00:21:28,640 --> 00:21:29,640
I will miss you guys.

385
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:30,920
We will also miss you.

386
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:32,448
- Goodbye.
- Bye.

387
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,048
Let's go.

388
00:21:38,040 --> 00:21:39,320
Thank you, Dr. Tian.

389
00:21:39,320 --> 00:21:40,920
- It's okay.
- Goodbye.

390
00:21:43,680 --> 00:21:45,880
Tian Tian, congratulations.

391
00:21:45,880 --> 00:21:47,360
I heard you are pregnant with Shen Mi's child.

392
00:21:47,360 --> 00:21:49,160
What? That's not true.

393
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:50,432
It's a lie.

394
00:21:50,432 --> 00:21:51,720
Pregnant? Really?

395
00:21:52,280 --> 00:21:54,040
No, I'm not pregnant.

396
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:55,968
I can find it out if you are pregnant or not.

397
00:21:55,968 --> 00:21:57,056
Give me your hand.

398
00:21:57,056 --> 00:21:59,120
I've told you, it's a lie.

399
00:21:59,120 --> 00:22:00,840
Why are you gossiping like my aunt?

400
00:22:00,840 --> 00:22:02,280
- Go, go.
- Congratulations.

401
00:22:02,280 --> 00:22:04,200
- Go, go. Don't make a mess.
- Okay.

402
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:05,640
Why are you all gossiping?

403
00:22:05,640 --> 00:22:07,240
What's wrong? Oh my.

404
00:22:15,120 --> 00:22:17,000
There are no outsiders now.

405
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:19,080
Just tell me,

406
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:22,440
are you pregnant with Shen Mi's child?

407
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:23,760
You are just being cautious,

408
00:22:23,760 --> 00:22:26,080
so you don't tell them, right?

409
00:22:26,080 --> 00:22:28,160
No. I've been very clear with you,

410
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:29,160
and repeated it several times.

411
00:22:29,160 --> 00:22:30,600
I didn't have anything with him,

412
00:22:30,600 --> 00:22:32,220
and I'm not carrying his child.

413
00:22:32,220 --> 00:22:34,000
Can you trust me?

414
00:22:34,800 --> 00:22:38,080
Tian Tian, since you two are in love,

415
00:22:38,080 --> 00:22:39,240
getting pregnant before marriage

416
00:22:39,240 --> 00:22:40,800
is not a disgrace.

417
00:22:40,800 --> 00:22:43,360
And it can't be seen
within the first four months.

418
00:22:43,360 --> 00:22:45,040
You guys set the date to marry now.

419
00:22:45,040 --> 00:22:47,440
You can still wear wedding dress.

420
00:22:47,440 --> 00:22:48,720
No. I swear,

421
00:22:48,720 --> 00:22:50,600
if I, Tian Tian, am pregnant,

422
00:22:50,600 --> 00:22:52,560
Tianlin Hospital will shut down.

423
00:22:59,080 --> 00:23:01,740
That's a pretty poisonous swear.

424
00:23:01,740 --> 00:23:02,912
You trust me now, right?

425
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:07,360
Oh, no. Oh my.

426
00:23:07,360 --> 00:23:09,040
What are you doing?

427
00:23:11,520 --> 00:23:14,280
About this matter,

428
00:23:14,280 --> 00:23:16,000
I just…

429
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:18,760
I just told my sister-in-law.

430
00:23:18,760 --> 00:23:21,520
W-Why did you tell my mom?

431
00:23:21,520 --> 00:23:23,040
She said,

432
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:25,640
even if it's raining knives today,

433
00:23:25,640 --> 00:23:29,280
you and Shen Mi have to go home together.

434
00:23:31,560 --> 00:23:32,680
Go home together?

435
00:23:33,560 --> 00:23:34,560
Go home together?

436
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:47,620
My aunt can't hide anything.

437
00:23:47,620 --> 00:23:49,560
Don't worry about it. I have explained

438
00:23:49,560 --> 00:23:50,580
to my parents already.

439
00:23:50,580 --> 00:23:51,584
It's okay.

440
00:23:52,160 --> 00:23:53,280
I might as well go.

441
00:23:54,000 --> 00:23:56,220
I was a part of it, after all.

442
00:23:56,220 --> 00:23:57,560
And I have never

443
00:23:57,560 --> 00:23:59,440
visited the former director of the hospital

444
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:01,680
for so long.

445
00:24:02,240 --> 00:24:03,480
This is a good time to visit him.

446
00:24:05,600 --> 00:24:07,360
Then let me tell you,

447
00:24:07,360 --> 00:24:09,440
my mom

448
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:12,920
might not like you,

449
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:14,880
so if she says something unpleasant,

450
00:24:14,880 --> 00:24:16,880
do not take it personally.

451
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:18,700
I have a strong mind.

452
00:24:18,700 --> 00:24:20,680
I'm going to go get dressed
and come back to pick you up.

453
00:24:42,120 --> 00:24:44,400
Uncle and aunt, I am Shen Mi.

454
00:24:49,320 --> 00:24:51,640
Hello, I am Shen Mi.

455
00:24:52,800 --> 00:24:54,520
Uncle and aunt, I am Shen Mi.

456
00:24:55,080 --> 00:24:56,840
Here are some gifts I brought for you.

457
00:24:59,280 --> 00:25:01,000
Be natural and normal.

458
00:25:04,720 --> 00:25:05,824
Hello.

459
00:25:07,232 --> 00:25:08,288
I am Shen Mi.

460
00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:09,856
Yes…

461
00:25:11,080 --> 00:25:12,640
What's there to be nervous about?

462
00:25:14,760 --> 00:25:17,040
Hello, I am Shen Mi.

463
00:25:18,000 --> 00:25:19,072
Nice to meet you.

464
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:44,960
What are you laughing at?

465
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:47,160
I've never seen Shen Mi from Lvchuan

466
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:49,020
so nervous before.

467
00:25:49,020 --> 00:25:50,280
I hope you can understand

468
00:25:50,280 --> 00:25:51,560
the importance of this visit

469
00:25:51,560 --> 00:25:53,600
and the possible consequences.

470
00:25:53,600 --> 00:25:54,688
Alright, boss.

471
00:25:55,232 --> 00:25:56,320
If this visit

472
00:25:56,320 --> 00:25:57,440
ends up bad,

473
00:25:59,040 --> 00:26:01,240
you won't be able to stay
at my house anymore, do you get it?

474
00:26:01,240 --> 00:26:04,280
So you're worried you can't
spend time with me, right?

475
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,800
I'm just worry about grandpa…

476
00:26:07,800 --> 00:26:10,944
You are worried that you can't
explain it to grandpa. I got it.

477
00:26:11,800 --> 00:26:12,832
Let's go in.

478
00:26:15,720 --> 00:26:17,040
Tian Tian is back.

479
00:26:17,040 --> 00:26:18,760
- Mrs. Li.
- Long time no see.

480
00:26:19,360 --> 00:26:20,400
Your boyfriend?

481
00:26:21,240 --> 00:26:23,080
- Your boyfriend?
- Friend.

482
00:26:23,600 --> 00:26:24,672
- Hello.
- He's quite handsome.

483
00:26:34,320 --> 00:26:35,424
Mom.

484
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:38,112
Mr. Shen is here.

485
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:39,880
The boss is here.

486
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:41,560
Aunt.

487
00:26:41,560 --> 00:26:42,800
This time I came in a hurry.

488
00:26:42,800 --> 00:26:44,340
I don't know what you like,

489
00:26:44,340 --> 00:26:45,520
please accept this.

490
00:26:46,040 --> 00:26:47,580
Don't be that polite.

491
00:26:47,580 --> 00:26:48,960
Where are Yuxian and my dad?

492
00:26:49,840 --> 00:26:53,280
Tian. Come down now.

493
00:26:53,280 --> 00:26:54,520
Tian Tian's boss is here.

494
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:16,280
Here come the delicious dishes.

495
00:27:17,280 --> 00:27:18,680
Here they come.

496
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:24,704
Here.

497
00:27:31,960 --> 00:27:32,960
Beggar's Chicken.

498
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:35,600
This Beggar's Chicken is incredible.

499
00:27:36,560 --> 00:27:37,632
Just so-so.

500
00:27:38,240 --> 00:27:40,480
Because we don't have all the equipment,

501
00:27:40,480 --> 00:27:43,200
so I used our oven,

502
00:27:43,200 --> 00:27:45,320
the taste might be a bit off.

503
00:27:46,640 --> 00:27:47,680
Shen.

504
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:49,640
I have been cooking for a lifetime.

505
00:27:49,640 --> 00:27:50,920
Compared to you,

506
00:27:50,920 --> 00:27:52,400
I really feel ashamed.

507
00:27:53,040 --> 00:27:54,440
Teach me when you have time.

508
00:27:54,440 --> 00:27:57,320
Your uncle Tian always criticizes me

509
00:27:57,320 --> 00:27:59,120
for making the same

510
00:27:59,120 --> 00:28:00,800
few homemade dishes.

511
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:05,040
What? I never do so.

512
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:08,160
Aunt,

513
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:10,440
it's hardest to make the homemade dishes well.

514
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:13,500
The taste of homemade dishes

515
00:28:13,500 --> 00:28:15,160
is the taste of mother.

516
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:17,240
Like when I was alone abroad,

517
00:28:17,240 --> 00:28:19,080
I just wanted to eat some homemade dishes,

518
00:28:19,080 --> 00:28:20,440
but I can't.

519
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:22,060
Until I got back to the country,

520
00:28:22,060 --> 00:28:25,400
my parents were busy making ends meet

521
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:27,000
and I don't have any siblings.

522
00:28:27,000 --> 00:28:28,480
I had an older brother before,

523
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:30,560
but unfortunately, we got separated later.

524
00:28:32,520 --> 00:28:34,200
I want to eat homemade dishes,

525
00:28:34,840 --> 00:28:36,320
but I can't.

526
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:39,840
Shen,

527
00:28:39,840 --> 00:28:41,160
I feel so upset

528
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:43,360
hearing it.

529
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:45,344
Don't worry.

530
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:47,520
If you want to eat homemade dishes,

531
00:28:47,520 --> 00:28:49,160
you are always welcome. Right, mom?

532
00:28:51,320 --> 00:28:55,160
Yes, Shen, you can come anytime

533
00:28:55,160 --> 00:28:56,480
when you're free.

534
00:28:57,280 --> 00:28:59,480
Alright, aunt. Then I'll come more often.

535
00:29:00,120 --> 00:29:02,340
Great, welcome.

536
00:29:02,340 --> 00:29:03,680
I'm going to serve the food.

537
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:06,528
Mom.

538
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:08,608
Hurry up.

539
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:12,200
Mr. Shen, Tian, dinner is ready.

540
00:29:12,200 --> 00:29:13,280
Come on, let's have the meal.

541
00:29:13,280 --> 00:29:14,368
Please.

542
00:29:16,864 --> 00:29:17,880
Here.

543
00:29:17,880 --> 00:29:18,960
Here, Uncle.

544
00:29:18,960 --> 00:29:20,080
Eat a little less.

545
00:29:21,360 --> 00:29:22,432
Here, Yuxian.

546
00:29:23,600 --> 00:29:24,840
Aunt, here is a piece for you.

547
00:29:24,840 --> 00:29:25,888
Thank you.

