00:29:29,280 --> 00:29:31,440
This piece is yours.

549
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:40,840
This piece is mine.

550
00:29:42,000 --> 00:29:45,020
Mr. Shen, don't be shy and eat.

551
00:29:45,020 --> 00:29:46,120
Make yourself at home.

552
00:29:49,080 --> 00:29:50,320
This one tastes good.

553
00:29:51,480 --> 00:29:52,640
Tian Tian, how do you know

554
00:29:52,640 --> 00:29:53,720
it's my favorite?

555
00:29:55,480 --> 00:29:58,520
Tian Tian, Shen worked so hard.

556
00:29:58,520 --> 00:29:59,616
What are you doing?

557
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:02,400
You've been working hard, eat more.

558
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,000
You've been working hard.

559
00:30:06,560 --> 00:30:10,700
Shen, I heard you said
your parents run a business.

560
00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:12,200
What kind of business do they do?

561
00:30:12,200 --> 00:30:14,680
Right, you've never told us about your family.

562
00:30:16,080 --> 00:30:17,320
My family…

563
00:30:18,040 --> 00:30:21,160
It's just an ordinary family,
running some small business.

564
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:22,280
Busy making ends meet.

565
00:30:23,600 --> 00:30:24,760
Exactly,

566
00:30:24,760 --> 00:30:26,240
all ordinary families

567
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:29,240
are busy making ends meet.

568
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,560
Like us,

569
00:30:31,560 --> 00:30:33,240
we run a small pet hospital

570
00:30:33,240 --> 00:30:35,020
and are terribly busy.

571
00:30:35,020 --> 00:30:36,360
Right, mom.

572
00:30:36,360 --> 00:30:38,420
And if Mr. Shen hadn't helped us this time,

573
00:30:38,420 --> 00:30:39,960
our hospital would have shut down.

574
00:30:40,720 --> 00:30:43,160
Mr. Shen, here, eat more meat

575
00:30:44,920 --> 00:30:46,520
and this osmanthus lotus root.

576
00:30:46,520 --> 00:30:47,584
It's really delicious.

577
00:31:20,800 --> 00:31:22,280
- I'll help you.
- No.

578
00:31:22,280 --> 00:31:23,440
You go out and take a break.

579
00:31:25,600 --> 00:31:28,360
There's too much fire out there.
I'll take a rest here.

580
00:31:29,280 --> 00:31:30,800
Too much fire?

581
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:33,720
Who told me this visit is important

582
00:31:33,720 --> 00:31:34,880
and have to take it very seriously?

583
00:31:35,760 --> 00:31:37,640
My mom, Shen Chen,

584
00:31:37,640 --> 00:31:40,000
and Tian Yuxian got you scared, right?

585
00:31:42,520 --> 00:31:43,760
How is that possible?

586
00:31:48,120 --> 00:31:49,120
Come on.

587
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:05,000
How is it, uncle?

588
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:06,140
Pretty good.

589
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:07,280
You've worked hard.

590
00:32:07,280 --> 00:32:09,040
- No problem.
- Shen.

591
00:32:09,880 --> 00:32:11,580
Stop and take a break.

592
00:32:11,580 --> 00:32:13,320
- Have an apple.
- No.

593
00:32:13,320 --> 00:32:15,160
I-I'll eat it after massaging uncle.

594
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:18,336
Mr. Shen.

595
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:21,480
Since you're here, let me ask you

596
00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:23,520
if this kid is doing nothing

597
00:32:23,520 --> 00:32:25,400
and holding you back

598
00:32:25,920 --> 00:32:27,160
at the hospital.

599
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:29,632
Aunt.

600
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:31,328
He is.

601
00:32:31,328 --> 00:32:34,440
<i>Shen Mi, remember this.</i>

602
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:37,280
<i>You brat, how dare you asked Shen Chen to come.</i>

603
00:32:39,600 --> 00:32:41,280
When he first came into the hospital,

604
00:32:42,040 --> 00:32:44,480
Yuxian indeed had a short temper,

605
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:45,880
and didn't follow management.

606
00:32:46,720 --> 00:32:49,400
<i>Shen Mi, you don't want
to be with my sister, right?</i>

607
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:53,240
But then, as time goes by,

608
00:32:53,240 --> 00:32:55,080
he has grown up a lot

609
00:32:55,080 --> 00:32:56,760
and now he's getting better and better.

610
00:32:57,360 --> 00:32:59,880
He takes special care of all the hospital pets,

611
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:01,720
especially when he grooms them.

612
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:03,720
<i>You're good.</i>

613
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:08,360
Aunt, all his progress now is for the hospital.

614
00:33:08,360 --> 00:33:09,640
And he knows

615
00:33:09,640 --> 00:33:12,040
he has put in a lot of effort.

616
00:33:12,040 --> 00:33:15,320
I think he's really great now.

617
00:33:16,640 --> 00:33:20,240
Mr. Shen, I have something to say.

618
00:33:20,240 --> 00:33:22,840
It's just so late,

619
00:33:22,840 --> 00:33:25,240
maybe you should go back with Tian Tian.

620
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:26,600
Is it okay for Carlo to be home alone?

621
00:33:28,080 --> 00:33:32,280
Right, Shen reminded me.

622
00:33:33,240 --> 00:33:35,540
Mr. Shen, look.

623
00:33:35,540 --> 00:33:37,520
Tian Tian has been living with you

624
00:33:37,520 --> 00:33:39,360
as Carlo's personal doctor

625
00:33:39,360 --> 00:33:40,960
for quite some time.

626
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:44,080
But after all, it's not good for
a man and a woman living in the same house.

627
00:33:44,720 --> 00:33:46,980
And this time there is a rumor of pregnancy.

628
00:33:46,980 --> 00:33:50,300
Even though we already know
it was a misunderstanding,

629
00:33:50,300 --> 00:33:54,040
it's not very convenient in the long run.

630
00:33:56,608 --> 00:33:57,696
Well,

631
00:33:58,200 --> 00:34:00,480
I have a solution that works both ways.

632
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:02,240
Tell me about it.

633
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:06,680
I could replace Tian Tian

634
00:34:07,360 --> 00:34:09,000
and move into Mr. Shen's house.

635
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:10,016
No way.

636
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:13,520
Why not?

637
00:34:13,520 --> 00:34:15,600
I think it's a good idea.

638
00:34:16,239 --> 00:34:18,360
Besides, Shen is a pet doctor

639
00:34:18,960 --> 00:34:20,360
with excellent medical skills,

640
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:22,719
he could easily take care of a dog.

641
00:34:22,719 --> 00:34:24,280
He…

642
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,440
I have one more thing to say.

643
00:34:30,199 --> 00:34:32,280
Since uncle, aunt and brother are all here.

644
00:34:32,960 --> 00:34:35,760
Tian Tian, I also want to
be a part of your family.

645
00:34:44,520 --> 00:34:46,800
<i>Bro, you are so brave. Amazing.</i>

646
00:34:48,880 --> 00:34:50,320
Uncle, Aunt.

647
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:51,320
In fact,

648
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:53,920
I have two things to clarify this time.

649
00:34:55,159 --> 00:34:58,280
One is about the misunderstanding
about Tian Tian's pregnancy,

650
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:59,320
I wanted to come and apologize.

651
00:34:59,320 --> 00:35:00,520
There's something more important

652
00:35:00,520 --> 00:35:02,280
I'd like to tell you,

653
00:35:05,120 --> 00:35:06,640
Tian Tian and I have been dating.

654
00:35:07,200 --> 00:35:08,256
Dating?

655
00:35:12,200 --> 00:35:14,760
<i>What? It's so dramatic.</i>

656
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:28,680
Shen, actually I really like you a lot

657
00:35:29,240 --> 00:35:31,760
and I hope that Tian Tian could be with you.

658
00:35:32,520 --> 00:35:34,520
But about the relationship thing,

659
00:35:34,520 --> 00:35:36,000
no one can force it.

660
00:35:38,680 --> 00:35:40,360
You're such a good boy.

661
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:42,160
I believe that you would definitely

662
00:35:42,160 --> 00:35:43,960
find your own happiness in the future.

663
00:35:47,560 --> 00:35:48,680
Aunt, you can go home.

664
00:35:48,680 --> 00:35:50,320
- Okay.
- I'm leaving then.

665
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:51,400
Be careful.

666
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:56,640
Go home, Aunt.

667
00:36:18,160 --> 00:36:19,200
Thank you today.

668
00:36:21,240 --> 00:36:22,272
Thank you.

669
00:36:24,920 --> 00:36:25,980
For what?

670
00:36:25,980 --> 00:36:29,160
I know you just said so to my parents

671
00:36:30,080 --> 00:36:32,280
to help me out.

672
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:33,312
Thank you.

673
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:38,200
<i>Tell me about you and Han Mengnan.</i>

674
00:36:38,760 --> 00:36:40,320
<i>When I was little,</i>

675
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:42,320
<i>I always thought that when I grew up,</i>

676
00:36:42,320 --> 00:36:44,000
<i>I must marry Mengnan.</i>

677
00:36:50,280 --> 00:36:51,400
Right?

678
00:36:54,520 --> 00:36:55,584
Yes.

679
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:58,520
If you're not around,

680
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:00,880
grandpa would be worried.

681
00:37:20,720 --> 00:37:21,824
What are you thinking?

682
00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:26,600
I feel

683
00:37:27,120 --> 00:37:28,760
my parents are getting old.

684
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,920
My mom is a housewife,

685
00:37:34,680 --> 00:37:37,600
a profession that is often overlooked

686
00:37:37,600 --> 00:37:39,600
and hard to get recognized.

687
00:37:40,240 --> 00:37:43,200
She has put all the best things in her life

688
00:37:44,040 --> 00:37:45,920
into this family.

689
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:50,720
My dad was a real career freak.

690
00:37:51,600 --> 00:37:54,480
But this illness has changed him a lot.

691
00:37:57,120 --> 00:37:59,648
Don't worry, he'll get better.

692
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:04,920
You'd stay with your dad tonight.

693
00:38:06,840 --> 00:38:07,936
Thank you.

694
00:38:11,240 --> 00:38:12,800
Actually, I quite envy you

695
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:15,960
to have such a complete and happy family

696
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:19,200
and your parents love you so much.

697
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:22,800
It's something I'll never get in my life.

698
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:30,496
Shen Mi.

699
00:38:31,680 --> 00:38:33,560
Happiness and completeness

700
00:38:34,160 --> 00:38:35,680
are not equal.

701
00:38:37,120 --> 00:38:38,640
A happy family

702
00:38:38,640 --> 00:38:40,240
does not just fall from the sky

703
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:41,680
on anyone.

704
00:38:42,600 --> 00:38:44,180
It also requires the family

705
00:38:44,180 --> 00:38:46,700
to work hard little by little

706
00:38:46,700 --> 00:38:50,160
in many years of getting along.

707
00:39:09,760 --> 00:39:11,800
If you really want a happy family,

708
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:13,520
you can start

709
00:39:14,240 --> 00:39:15,320
with yourself.

710
00:39:47,120 --> 00:39:48,160
Mom.

711
00:39:48,960 --> 00:39:50,360
What are you doing knitting
in the middle of the night?

712
00:39:50,360 --> 00:39:52,160
You are back. Sit down.

713
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:53,200
What are you knitting?

714
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:57,056
I am knitting you gloves. Come on.

715
00:40:00,360 --> 00:40:01,408
Try them on.

716
00:40:03,240 --> 00:40:06,120
I told you knitting at night hurts your eyes.

717
00:40:06,120 --> 00:40:08,000
And I can't use them anymore
when it gets warmer.

718
00:40:09,160 --> 00:40:10,960
Well, wait till winter.

719
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:14,220
I have nothing to do at home alone anyway.

720
00:40:14,220 --> 00:40:15,800
If I don't do something,

721
00:40:15,800 --> 00:40:17,240
I would be so bored.

722
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:23,040
Have you been sleeping well lately, mom?

723
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:27,880
I'll take you to see
a Chinese medicine doctor some other day.

724
00:40:31,400 --> 00:40:33,320
Why didn't Mengnan come back with you?

725
00:40:35,600 --> 00:40:36,608
Mengnan…

726
00:40:37,200 --> 00:40:38,800
She's busy,

727
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:39,800
couldn't come today.

728
00:40:41,680 --> 00:40:43,480
You've all grown so big.

729
00:40:44,840 --> 00:40:46,240
Look at this yard,

730
00:40:47,600 --> 00:40:48,960
I think I can still hear

731
00:40:48,960 --> 00:40:50,440
the sound of you and Mengnan

732
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:52,440
laughing and joking around here
when you were little.

733
00:40:54,400 --> 00:40:56,280
In fact, about you and Mengnan,

734
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:58,820
it all started with your dad and secretary Han.

735
00:40:58,820 --> 00:41:00,560
I didn't expect you guys
would actually be a couple.

736
00:41:04,600 --> 00:41:06,920
In fact, my biggest wish now

737
00:41:06,920 --> 00:41:09,120
is to see you two get married soon,

738
00:41:09,120 --> 00:41:10,680
so I can have my grandchild.

739
00:41:13,040 --> 00:41:14,112
Our family

740
00:41:14,720 --> 00:41:15,980
hasn't been so lively

741
00:41:15,980 --> 00:41:17,360
for many years.

742
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:23,008
Mom.

743
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:24,960
Actually,

744
00:41:25,760 --> 00:41:27,200
Mengnan and I…

745
00:41:27,200 --> 00:41:29,080
What happened? Is everything okay?

746
00:41:29,800 --> 00:41:30,816
Nothing.

747
00:41:31,800 --> 00:41:33,160
We're just

748
00:41:34,120 --> 00:41:36,000
childhood friends.

749
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:38,800
We were so young

750
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:40,840
to know about love, right?

751
00:41:43,080 --> 00:41:45,280
It's just some game.

752
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:46,720
What?

753
00:41:46,720 --> 00:41:48,720
I saw clearly at that time

754
00:41:48,720 --> 00:41:50,540
that you really like Mengnan,

755
00:41:50,540 --> 00:41:52,120
and in my heart,

756
00:41:52,120 --> 00:41:54,080
I've already considered Mengnan
as my daughter-in-law.

757
00:42:34,816 --> 00:42:38,336
<i>♫ Your gaze is unwavering ♫</i>

758
00:42:40,352 --> 00:42:44,896
<i>♫ Only enough to accommodate me ♫</i>

759
00:42:46,112 --> 00:42:50,784
<i>♫ I have been melted by you countless times ♫</i>

760
00:42:51,744 --> 00:42:55,296
<i>♫ Yet I'm at a loss for what to do ♫</i>

761
00:42:57,248 --> 00:43:00,192
<i>♫ I can only hold on to you ♫</i>

762
00:43:02,272 --> 00:43:06,176
<i>♫ Now you are still with me ♫</i>

763
00:43:07,840 --> 00:43:12,096
<i>♫ Traveling through time together ♫</i>

764
00:43:13,952 --> 00:43:21,888
<i>♫ Someday, I'll be completely
forgotten by the world ♫</i>

765
00:43:21,888 --> 00:43:25,088
<i>♫ Leaving no trace ♫</i>

766
00:43:25,088 --> 00:43:29,120
<i>♫ Only you will still remember ♫</i>

767
00:43:30,880 --> 00:43:33,184
<i>♫ My appearance ♫</i>
